description: Pure Coolness [2007 - Kyrgyzstan] Boz salkyn Боз салкын Drama http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1050089/ Beautiful Asema, a young Kyrgyz girl from the city, against her parents' wishes, makes a trip with her fiancé, Murat, to his rural village home. Murat's family try to force them to marry immediately, however, the young couple want to wait until the autumn. But in the remote, mountainous villages of Kyrgyzstan, the ancient custom of Ala Kachuu (bride stealing) still exists. Is it possible to justify this tradition today, even if husband and wife eventually live happily ever after? So popular was this film in Kyrgyzstan, in 2007, twenty percent of newborn girls were named Asema.
